/******************************************************************************                      
** Name		 : USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryStatus                      
** Short Desc:  To get Beneficiary Status
**                      
** Full Description:   To get Beneficiary Status. This sp uses Innotrust response data from table 
					   TBL_PP_STG_InnoTrustValidationEngineInput for validation.            
**        
**                              
** Input Arguments: 
@UserID INT,
@Type Bit =1--auto

**         
** Sample Call     

EXEC USP_PP_GetValidationEngineBeneficiaryStatus  1,0     
                 	
**                      
** Standard declarations                      
**       SET LOCK_TIMEOUT         30000   -- 30 seconds                      
**                       
** Created By: Debajyoti kalita   
** Company   : Kaspick & Company                      
